metatags.twitter:title: Graham County Chamber of Commerce - Coming soon to you and your...
metatags.og:title: Graham County Chamber of Commerce - Coming soon to you and your customers: Arizona Mobile ID App.  A convenient, secure and contactless digital ID on your smartphone has been in the works for several years and now the Arizona Department of Transportation (ADOT) is excited to announce the soon-to-launch Arizona Mobile ID App (mID). This innovative app will transform how residents prove their identity, and we’d like to provide you with information on how mID works and how you can integrate it into your identity verification processes.   While you will start to see customers using the Arizona Mobile ID app, please be aware that the MVD is urging people to continue to carry their physical, plastic credential. And MVD will continue to issue physical credentials. That’s because using this technology is voluntary. Customers may choose to have it, and we expect more and more people to embrace this technology in the future. But, as with any innovation, it will take time for it to become more familiar to consumers.
